data.description: Inviting 1-bedroom, 1-bath condo spanning 694 sq ft with an open floorplan and ample natural light. Highlighted by a wood-burning fireplace in the great room, the kitchen showcases white Shaker cabinets, granite countertops, an attractive tile backsplash, and stainless steel appliances. The primary bedroom is generously sized with a walk-in closet, complemented by stunning LVP flooring throughout. Step out from the great room to a charming patio with storage. Community amenities include 2 pools, a fitness center, tennis courts, and trails. Conveniently situated in the heart of Kingstowne, close to all amenities.
